<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h2>Sign Up Form</h2>
      <form class="signup">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputFN">First Name</label>
          <input type="firstName" class="form-control" id="firstname-input" placeholder="First Name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputLN">Last Name</label>
          <input type="lastName" class="form-control" id="lastname-input" placeholder="Last Name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputLN">City</label>
          <input type="cityName" class="form-control" id="cityname-input" placeholder="City">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputLN">State</label>
          <input type="stateName" class="form-control" id="statename-input" placeholder="State">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email-input" placeholder="Email">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Password</label>
          <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password-input" placeholder="Password">
        </div>
        <div style="display: none" id="alert" class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Error:</span> <span class="msg"></span>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Sign Up</button>
      </form>
      <br />
      <p>Or log in <a href="/login">here</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p>
        Long ago, there was a website created that made space for people to meet online, share their interests, and
        hopefully meet in person one day.
        It was called MySpace and it actually worked.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>